snippet.title: 🌍Universal Thief 🐱‍👤 - Full playthrough
snippet.description:
Have you ever wanted to steal absolutely EVERYTHING? Well now you can! We hope you will use this power for GOOD, and not spiral into an uncontrollable power trip. Have fun!

https://adriendittrick.itch.io/universal-thief

This game was made in 48h by Shinlalala (art) and me (code,music) for GMTK jam 2020
